Central Bank of Djibouti (French: Banque Centrale de Djibouta) bụ ikike ego nke Djibouti.  Ọ bụ ya na-ahụ maka ijikwa ego obodo, franc Djibouti, yana ọnọdụ mgbanwe mba ofesi na ndekọ ndekọ ego nke mba.
Ebumnuche nke Central Bank of Djibouti gụnyere:
Ụlọ akụ ahụ na-ahụ maka gọọmentị Djibouti.  E hiwere ya site na iwu 79030 nke 18 Eprel 1979.
